 &quot;Those are good odds.&quot; She said softly as the rain came pouring down. &quot;We will need their help as time closer. The moon will be at its darkest day after tommorow. That is when we will strike fear and death into the very hearts of the Roman men. The ways that have placed fear into the hearts of others and that made us who we are will be used once more.&quot; <br>
<br>
She limped closer to the small fire that was going inside the shelter and sat down slowly. She looked up at her company. <br>
 &quot;In the darkest hour, Hippolyte will be rescued and death will once again be company to the Romans. I will need your four-legged friends to mask our arrival with the ancient calls of the wild. One thing that men are afraid of is the unknown. And that is when we will strike.&quot; She sighed softly. &quot;But first, we need to survey the village, see what is surrounding it, what hiding places there are and if there is a stream running nearby it.&quot; <br>
&quot;How many of us have horses?&quot; She asked softly. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solariwolf@amazonsunite>solariwolf</A> at: 4/13/03 7:55:03 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=odessaofpaphos>Odessa of Paphos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 203<br> <font color=#993300>(4/14/03 4:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=146>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/xvmegvxwpt/images/amarice_11.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Planning Begins</span><hr size=1> Odessa nodded, listening to Solari and spoke after she finished. <br>
